    ## Introduction and Data

    Our topic is UFO sightings.
  
  Our topic for this project is UFOs, or “Unidentified Flying Objects”. UFOs as proof of alien life are largely writen off as pseudoscience by the scientific community, but this does not take away from the fact that there are tens of thousands of sightings reported annually. 
In 2020, the Pentagon released videos of unidentified flying objects, sparking the intrigue of enthusiasts and skeptics alike. This is outlined in a New York Times article that also highlights how the government has been looking into unidentified aerial phenomena (UAF; another term for UFO) since the 1950s; articles like these add merit to our research into consistencies in examining UFOs worldwide.
Links to NYT article: https://www.nytimes.com/2020/04/28/us/pentagon-ufo-videos.html
